high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk to the shelf running along the floor in the recess in the wall.
Pick up the credit card to the right of the shelf.
Turn around and walk until you are even with the coffee table to your left and then turn to face it
Put the credit card on the square white plate.
Pick up the plate with the credit card on top of it.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the shelf.
Put the plate with the credit card on top of it on the shelf to the left of the box.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a credit card on top of it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and hang right to the black bench.
Pick up the credit card off the bench.
Turn around and walk to the short side of the table closest to you.
Put the credit card on the white plate.
Pick up the plate.
Turn around and walk right to get to the black bench.
Put the plate in a front and to the left of the box.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a credit card on it on a bench.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward past the coffee table, turn right, go forward to the black platform.
Take the credit card from the right side of the platform.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the coffee table.
Put the credit card on the white plate on the coffee table.
Take the plate from the coffee table.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn right, go forward to the black platform.
Put the plate on the right side of the platform between the box and the blue object and close to the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a credit card on it on a black platform.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the black bench.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the right side of the black bench.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up to the coffee table.
Put the credit card on the white plate that is on the coffee table.
Pick up the white plate with the credit card on it off of the coffee table.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the black bench.
Put the white plate with the credit card on it on the bench to the right of the blue vase.
anns.task_desc: Put a white plate with a credit card on it on a bench.

high_descs: Turn around then go to the right and walk straight to the black bench.
Pick up the credit card from off of the black bench.
Turn around, go straight then turn left to face the end of the coffee table.
Place the credit card on the plate on the coffee table.
Pick up the white plate from the coffee table.
Turn to the left and walk straight to the black bench.
Place the white plate on the left side of the black bench.
anns.task_desc: Move the white plate with the credit card on top of it the right side of the black bench.

high_descs: Turn left towards the chair and then walk to the grey table.
Pick up the credit card on the table.
Turn left and walk towards the door and then turn to the coffee table with the ash tray.
Place the credit card on the ash tray.
Pick up the ash tray with the credit card on it.
Turn left towards the wall and then walk back to the grey table.
Place the ash tray on the table near the cardboard box.
anns.task_desc: Put an ash tray with a credit card on it on the grey table.
